WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.446
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.446 --> 00:00:04.017
I have another video for you all today.

00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:15.400
I want to talk to you about being the friend of God and more so what that means to me, but what I feel in my heart that you all need to know.

00:00:15.782 --> 00:00:24.880
I pray for people, like I told you last video, whenever I talk to people on the phone, the Lord will reveal things to me about them.

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:35.120
It was interesting because I was asking the Lord about an individual and He said, "Brandon, I don't know them.

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:38.146
I used to know them, but I don't know them anymore.

00:00:38.519 --> 00:00:42.399
" That took me back and I said, "Well, Lord, what do you mean by that?

00:00:42.399 --> 00:00:45.825
" He said, "Brandon, how do you know somebody?

00:00:45.825 --> 00:00:48.520
How do you get to know somebody?

00:00:48.809 --> 00:00:52.251
" I said, "Well, Lord, you spend time with them.

00:00:52.251 --> 00:00:53.760
You're intimate with them.

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:59.987
" He said, "Do the people that watch your videos—you've made over 100 videos—do you feel like they know you?

00:01:01.827 --> 00:01:05.000
" I said, "No, Lord, they don't know me at all.

00:01:05.560 --> 00:01:18.627
They may know a lot about me, my history, and things that You've done for me, but do they truly know you?

00:01:23.511 --> 00:01:23.916
" I said, "No, not at all.

00:01:23.916 --> 00:01:34.330
" They don't know the intimacy that my wife and I have.

00:01:34.330 --> 00:01:36.284
How is that developed?

00:01:45.670 --> 00:01:54.590
It is developed day by day in intimacy and a friendship, just like a marriage is developed day by day.

00:01:54.590 --> 00:02:05.230
If you hear any noises, it's my daughter again, Megan; she's sitting in here watching VeggieTales.

00:02:19.111 --> 00:02:19.495
Intimacy is developed day by day; it is never an overnight thing.

00:02:34.073 --> 00:02:34.667
Like I said, you met your husband or your wife and you had a courtship.

00:02:36.447 --> 00:03:03.245
You were so excited to go on these dates and the relationship was fresh; you had those puppy dog eyes and you were excited to go out to the movies or go out to dinner.

00:03:23.150 --> 00:03:30.808
You have that relationship, that courtship, and you're excited about that relationship, but when you get married, there's an intimacy that develops beyond a boyfriend and girlfriend, beyond anything you can comprehend.

00:03:30.808 --> 00:03:51.220
Of course, if you've been married for a while, you know—I've been married 23 years—so you start to really know that individual: their likes, their facial expressions, the smells, everything.

00:04:00.359 --> 00:04:03.270
You know that individual, but it is developed over time; it is not developed in a day.

00:04:03.270 --> 00:04:12.910
So a lot of people think they go to church on a Sunday, and that's what the Lord shows me.

00:04:12.910 --> 00:04:24.457
They go to church on a Sunday, they may volunteer maybe once a month, and they have an hour service.

00:04:24.457 --> 00:04:39.365
They go to that hour service, they may pray for ten minutes a day, and they may read their Bible for five minutes a day.

00:04:52.006 --> 00:05:01.782
But just think about this: imagine if you did that exact same thing with your spouse or your loved one and you only talked to them five minutes a day.

00:05:01.782 --> 00:05:32.159
Your main conversation was about an hour on Sundays when you go to church; after that, you have some fellowship at dinner, and then you don't talk to them anymore but maybe five or ten minutes a day from then on—never on the phone, nothing—and you're doing all the talking.

00:05:32.159 --> 00:05:42.453
You're rehearsing everything that you want from them: "I need this and this and this.

00:05:44.880 --> 00:06:04.747
God, I thank you that you healed Johnny and you're healing Susie, and you're going after this one who is lost.

00:06:04.747 --> 00:06:19.959
Lord, I have all these needs, and I'm not feeling well in my body today.

00:06:19.959 --> 00:06:33.095
Lord, I have all this stuff going on at work; my boss is a real jerk and I've got this deadline.

00:06:33.095 --> 00:06:39.511
Could you help me with some money?

00:06:39.511 --> 00:06:52.916
" Then you turn around and say, "Amen," and then you're gone.

00:06:52.916 --> 00:07:11.000
He doesn't hear from you anymore that day other than when you need something again.

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:21.979
Every single time you go to the Lord, you need something again.

00:07:32.453 --> 00:07:32.867
You don't really ever hear His heart.

00:07:32.867 --> 00:07:46.701
Prayer is a two-way conversation; He's going to talk to you and you're going to talk to Him.

00:07:46.701 --> 00:07:52.573
But most people think prayer is just baby steps.

00:07:57.994 --> 00:08:02.240
This is like little children stuff: "Father, I need, I need, I need; I have wants and desires.

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:03.560
Bye!

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:17.709
" But if you want to grow up in the relationship and you want to come up to a higher place with Him...

00:08:17.709 --> 00:08:25.751
people say, "How do you see in the spirit?

00:08:25.751 --> 00:08:30.484
How do you have visitations from angels?

00:08:30.484 --> 00:08:35.908
How have you had eight visitations from Jesus?

00:08:35.908 --> 00:08:38.680
How have you seen into the throne room like that?

00:08:41.020 --> 00:08:51.120
I want you to help me to get there because I don't know how to get there.

00:08:56.705 --> 00:08:57.835
I don't hear God.

00:08:58.100 --> 00:09:09.475
" I read so many comments in the comment section from people asking me how to hear God.

00:09:09.475 --> 00:09:11.659
It is developed.

00:09:11.659 --> 00:09:25.887
It says, "Those that seek me will find me; those that knock, I'll open the door unto him.

00:09:25.887 --> 00:09:31.347
" Relationship is developed day to day, all day long.

00:09:32.907 --> 00:09:35.070
The Bible says to pray without ceasing.

00:09:35.070 --> 00:09:46.560
Seeking Him and finding Him automatically tells me that God is hiding in some way.

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:50.897
It's like hide and seek.

00:09:50.897 --> 00:09:53.741
"God, where are you?

00:09:54.846 --> 00:09:59.280
I want to be intimate with you.

00:10:11.316 --> 00:10:11.731
I want to go to another level.

00:10:11.731 --> 00:10:14.212
What's on your heart?

00:10:14.212 --> 00:10:22.906
" People ask if I pray a certain way to get Him to show me things.

00:10:22.906 --> 00:10:34.825
I want to say it like this: not one time do I ever pray with the intentions of seeking and seeing.

00:10:34.825 --> 00:10:39.829
If I pray, I'm praying because I'm intimate.

00:10:40.590 --> 00:10:43.133
I want to touch His garment.

00:10:53.148 --> 00:10:53.456
I want what's on His heart.

00:10:53.456 --> 00:11:00.426
"Lord, what's on your heart today?

00:11:00.426 --> 00:11:04.000
Let me help you.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:09.000
What is grieving you today?

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:14.700
What's your agenda, not my agenda?

00:11:14.700 --> 00:11:37.897
" I don't pray for Him to touch my agenda; I pray for His agenda for me, mirroring it back and saying, "God, not my will but Yours be done.

00:11:37.897 --> 00:11:44.445
" How can I come up higher in my thinking?

00:11:44.445 --> 00:11:50.160
The Bible says that you have the mind of Christ.

00:11:59.320 --> 00:11:59.514
You can think like Christ thinks by meditating on His word, getting scripture inside of you.

00:11:59.514 --> 00:12:17.215
I try very seldom to—and I'm just being real with y'all—I get in the flesh too and I go to him and say, "Lord, I have needs.

00:12:17.215 --> 00:12:20.697
I need my puppies to sell.

00:12:20.932 --> 00:12:23.655
I need all this stuff.

00:12:25.639 --> 00:12:32.475
" But He said He knows you have need of things before you even ask.

00:12:32.475 --> 00:12:44.459
Jesus said, "Our Father, who art in heaven, hallowed be thy name.

00:12:44.459 --> 00:12:51.855
Thy kingdom come, thy will be done.

00:12:56.720 --> 00:12:57.743
" He knows everything you need before you even ask it.

00:12:57.743 --> 00:13:04.450
So I go to Him not insulting Him, but thanking Him for it.

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:09.009
"Thank you, Father, for healing for my family.

00:13:09.009 --> 00:13:15.508
No colds, no viruses, no nothing come nigh.

00:13:15.508 --> 00:13:29.645
I thank you, Father, that your word says that by your stripes we are healed.

00:13:29.645 --> 00:13:36.160
I thank you, Father, that you said in your word that those that seek you will find you.

00:13:36.160 --> 00:13:52.320
Now, Father, whatever is on your heart today, I thank you that I pray the mysteries and the secret things.

00:13:52.320 --> 00:14:30.060
And if you have anything to show me today, Lord, not in the flesh, I thank you that I see what I'm supposed to see and I hear what I'm supposed to hear from You, that You said I will hear Your voice and a stranger's voice I'll not follow.

00:14:30.060 --> 00:14:39.060
Now, Satan, I bind you in the name of Jesus and I command you to bow your knee.

00:14:45.920 --> 00:14:46.270
You get out of here, you leave me alone.

00:14:49.644 --> 00:15:02.753
I plead the blood over my prayer time and I plead the blood over me that I hear the Lord's voice and I'm not going to be tormented by the tormentor.

00:15:04.409 --> 00:15:06.360
" I go to Him with worship.

00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:12.669
What really blesses me is Kim Clement.

00:15:12.669 --> 00:15:24.888
He has worship things on YouTube and I listen to him worshiping on "The Mountain of the Lord.

00:15:24.888 --> 00:15:37.909
" I record it on my phone and I put it on repeat, just hearing him talk about the mountain of the Lord.

00:15:37.909 --> 00:15:54.879
I feel the presence of the Lord so strong whenever that man sings, and he went home to be with the Lord years ago.

00:15:54.879 --> 00:16:02.360
I listen to that and I listen to piano music, like "I Surrender All.

00:16:17.420 --> 00:16:18.015
" You just get in the presence of the Lord.

00:16:18.015 --> 00:16:24.687
Find what ministers to you and gets you in that river.

00:16:24.687 --> 00:16:29.400
Think about Lot in Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:16:29.400 --> 00:16:31.868
Lot was Abraham's nephew.

00:16:31.868 --> 00:16:52.827
He's in the midst of all the trash going on and doesn't even know that Sodom and Gomorrah is about to be judged and wiped off the face of the Earth.

00:16:52.827 --> 00:16:57.799
But God comes to Abraham because he's His friend.

00:16:57.799 --> 00:17:06.720
God will come to you and start speaking to you and showing you the hidden things.

00:17:06.720 --> 00:17:27.026
There's a lot of things I probably shouldn't say on here, but out of compassion, I try to tell you all what's coming and what to pray about.

00:17:27.026 --> 00:17:32.560
Some of this stuff people are not ready for.

00:17:32.560 --> 00:17:47.493
There are some of you that are mature and understand, but there are a lot of babies on here that don't know, so I'm trying to take you to the next level, teaching you about being a friend of God.

00:17:47.493 --> 00:18:09.240
When the Bible says that Jesus says, "Depart from me, I never knew you," people say, "Lord, I healed the sick in your name and cast out devils in your name.

00:18:09.240 --> 00:18:12.080
" But He says to you at the end, "Depart from me, I never knew you.

00:18:12.080 --> 00:18:13.989
" He never knew you.

00:18:13.989 --> 00:18:21.570
That means you can have a relationship with somebody and talk to them, but they don't know you.

00:18:24.076 --> 00:18:28.480
You can have a conversation at church, but you still don't know Him.

00:18:32.501 --> 00:18:45.335
You probably do not know your pastor; he preaches at you for an hour every Sunday, but you don't know his intimacy behind closed doors.

00:18:49.736 --> 00:19:06.686
You can get to know the Father in a relationship that deep, where He will come and start sharing the hidden things and the secret things that He won't talk about to anybody else.

00:19:06.686 --> 00:19:12.324
He'll start sharing intimate things because it was developed out of relationship.

00:19:18.502 --> 00:19:18.799
You have a different relationship with every child you have.

00:19:18.799 --> 00:19:30.499
You love them all, but you might not be a friend to all of them.

00:19:35.183 --> 00:19:35.480
A friendship is developed.

00:19:35.480 --> 00:19:40.550
It's about who wants to spend more time with me.

00:19:48.524 --> 00:19:53.684
Does that child sit around and say, "Dad, let's go have a coffee or play outside"?

00:19:53.684 --> 00:19:59.619
They're always asking to be at your feet.

00:19:59.619 --> 00:20:17.453
That is a lot different than the one saying, "I'm going to hang out with my friends, I'll see you in a week.

00:20:17.453 --> 00:20:23.131
" I hope this makes sense.

00:20:23.131 --> 00:20:35.405
Going deeper in the relationship with Him is like a marriage.

00:20:35.405 --> 00:20:49.255
If you don't spend time with your spouse, you are not going to be intimate.

00:20:57.040 --> 00:21:01.484
The more time you spend with them, the more you talk to them and understand them.

00:21:05.280 --> 00:21:14.829
You have hours of conversations because you love them and you have this burning desire to know them.

00:21:14.829 --> 00:21:19.891
It's time for you to come up higher.

00:21:19.891 --> 00:21:37.919
People want to know about the intimacy of seeing into the spirit and seeing angels, but it doesn't come with a shallow relationship; it comes with a refiner's fire.

00:21:37.919 --> 00:21:43.063
A good marriage is always tested.

00:21:43.063 --> 00:22:08.240
It's when you go through the fire with that person that you put a pull on the chain, and the stronger the chain, the more it will last.

00:22:08.240 --> 00:22:34.000
When you go through the trials of life and spiritual pressure from the demonic and you're still strong and say, "Father, though this tries to slay me, yet will I praise You.

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:36.016
No matter how hard this trial is, I worship You.

00:22:36.544 --> 00:22:38.380
I keep my eyes on You.

00:22:41.463 --> 00:22:52.520
I will not be moved by what I see or feel; I'm moved by what the word of God says.

00:22:52.520 --> 00:23:02.140
" Keeping your eyes on Him when you're hurting and broken, and you just keep pushing and being real with Him—when you get real with God, God will get real with you.

00:23:21.690 --> 00:23:22.145
He knows the secrets and the intents of your heart.

00:23:22.145 --> 00:23:35.783
When you go to Him in prayer without an agenda, it's like talking to your spouse.

00:23:35.783 --> 00:23:47.840
If you were talking to your wife and looking at your watch or phone every five minutes, it's boring.

00:23:47.840 --> 00:24:01.863
But if you lose track of time while worshiping and an hour feels like five minutes, that's love.

00:24:01.863 --> 00:24:10.390
That's the way it is when you're passionately in love and pursuing them.

00:24:10.390 --> 00:24:25.813
When He says, "I don't know them," and yet they say they're a Christian, that's a very scary place to be.

00:24:25.813 --> 00:24:31.480
Does the Father know you, or does He just know a lot about you?

00:24:31.480 --> 00:24:42.291
Do you casually converse with Him for ten minutes with an agenda of what you need?

00:24:42.291 --> 00:24:50.975
He loves you and desires intimacy, just like He did with Abraham.

00:24:50.975 --> 00:25:03.470
David was a man after God's own heart; he was passionately in love with the Lord.

00:25:03.470 --> 00:25:17.093
He was a warrior—a man's man who killed lions and bears—yet he had such compassion and intimacy with the Father.

00:25:17.093 --> 00:25:32.873
You read Psalms and see this guy had it; he was quick to repent and always loving on the Father.

00:25:32.873 --> 00:25:39.520
That was under the Old Covenant; we have a New Covenant with Jesus.

00:25:39.520 --> 00:25:53.720
Think of how much deeper we can have a relationship and the glory of the Lord can rest on your household.

00:25:59.084 --> 00:26:02.674
I want to go deeper with the Father in 2024.

00:26:02.674 --> 00:26:07.924
Where will it be in 2025?

00:26:07.924 --> 00:26:17.457
Will He start showing you the secret things and reveal to you witty ideas and revelations?

00:26:17.457 --> 00:26:22.571
Let me pray for you all today.

00:26:22.571 --> 00:26:31.943
Father, I thank you for every person watching this.

00:26:31.943 --> 00:26:47.419
I pray a hedge of protection on them, that they would be intimate with You and You would call them a friend.

00:26:49.339 --> 00:26:59.100
We want to be on fire for Jesus, and our relationship should reflect You.

00:26:59.100 --> 00:27:21.940
I thank you for taking these people to another level of knowing You, that Your word would become Rhema to their minds, bodies, and spirits.

00:27:28.189 --> 00:27:31.146
I thank you for every single one of them.

00:27:39.383 --> 00:27:39.777
For the people who've blessed me, I pray over their finances.

00:27:39.777 --> 00:27:51.559
I thank you for better jobs, creative ideas to get wealth, bonuses, sales, and growth in business.

00:27:51.559 --> 00:27:59.519
I call healing and wholeness over their bodies.

00:27:59.519 --> 00:28:08.080
I speak to thyroids to be healed and whole in Jesus' name.

00:28:08.080 --> 00:28:12.286
They're delivered from satanic bondage.

00:28:27.760 --> 00:28:28.120
I call for cataracts of the eyes to be healed and creative miracles in their eyes.

00:28:28.120 --> 00:28:40.011
I call for physical and spiritual ears to open right now with new hairs and new follicles.

00:28:40.011 --> 00:28:49.589
I speak to arthritis to go; Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:28:55.366 --> 00:28:55.760
We speak to gallbladders and stomach issues.

00:28:55.760 --> 00:29:09.457
We curse colon cancer in the name of Jesus and command it to go now.

00:29:09.457 --> 00:29:14.860
We call for restoration in marriages and relationships with children.

00:29:14.860 --> 00:29:22.829
We thank you for new houses, new homes, and new cars.

00:29:22.829 --> 00:29:33.286
I thank you for better-paying jobs for them right now in Jesus' name.

00:29:40.650 --> 00:29:44.813
We take authority over demonic spirits in the workplace and command them to cease and be still.

00:29:54.869 --> 00:29:55.179
We plead the blood of Jesus over their work environment.

00:29:58.260 --> 00:30:06.022
We thank you that Your angels are going before us and protecting us by the blood.

00:30:17.933 --> 00:30:18.306
We pray for truck drivers, EMTs, hospital workers, and for the police.

00:30:18.306 --> 00:30:31.780
Show them hidden things from criminals and protect our officers, our sheriffs, and the Department of Homeland Security.

00:30:31.780 --> 00:30:51.192
We pray for our borders, that You would keep the riff-raff out and the people trying to cause harm or trafficking children.

00:30:58.399 --> 00:31:07.737
I pray a protection over this nation and that You rise up and call this nation blessed.

00:31:07.737 --> 00:31:13.555
We thank you that Jesus is coming soon for us.

00:31:13.555 --> 00:31:35.429
We want intimacy with You and we thank you that we get to spend eternity crying, "Holy, holy, holy is the Lord.

00:31:36.734 --> 00:31:40.560
" Thank you, Lord, for always meeting our needs and taking care of my family.

00:31:48.305 --> 00:31:48.760
In Jesus' name, amen.

00:31:59.427 --> 00:32:03.785
Well, I just wanted to thank you all for watching.

00:32:08.639 --> 00:32:13.799
If this video blessed you, please click that like and subscribe button.

00:32:16.459 --> 00:32:23.350
You are helping get the gospel throughout the world.

00:32:31.280 --> 00:32:33.680
Thank you for your support and your love.

00:32:39.679 --> 00:32:42.626
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:32:42.626 --> 00:32:51.034
Jesus loves you so much and we will see you next time.

00:32:56.039 --> 00:32:59.039
Bye-bye.
